    {
      "name": "3. Deposit Operations",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Manual Deposit (100 COIN)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Response has ledger_txn_id\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('ledger_txn_id');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('new_balance');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"ledger_txn_id\", jsonData.ledger_txn_id);",
                  "    console.log(\"New balance: \" + jsonData.new_balance);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Id",
                "value": "{{admin_user_id}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Role",
                "value": "ADMIN"
              },
              {
                "key": "Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "deposit-manual-100-{{$timestamp}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"wallet_id\": \"{{wallet_id}}\",\n  \"amount\": 100,\n  \"currency\": \"COIN\",\n  \"type\": \"manual_deposit\",\n  \"ref_type\": \"admin_adjustment\",\n  \"ref_id\": \"adj-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"meta_json\": {\n    \"reason\": \"Testing wallet deposit\",\n    \"admin_id\": \"{{admin_user_id}}\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/wallets/{{wallet_id}}/deposit",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "wallets", "{{wallet_id}}", "deposit"]
            },
            "description": "Deposits 100 COIN into the wallet.\n\n**Spec:** specs/wallet/wallet.pillar.v2.yml lines 756-839\n\n**Permissions:** wallet:admin, wallet:manage\n\n**Idempotency:** Via Idempotency-Key header\n\n**Double-Entry Flow:**\n1. Debit system account (id=1) -100 COIN\n2. Credit user account +100 COIN\n3. Update wallet_balance_snapshot\n\n**Events Emitted:**\n- WALLET_CREDITED\n- LEDGER_TRANSACTION_CREATED"
          },
          "response": []
        },
