    {
      "name": "7. Idempotency Tests",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Same Wallet Twice (Idempotent)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 201\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Returns same wallet_id on duplicate\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log(\"Wallet ID: \" + jsonData.wallet_id);",
                  "    console.log(\"Note: Call this request multiple times. The wallet_id should remain the same.\");",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Id",
                "value": "{{admin_user_id}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Role",
                "value": "ADMIN"
              },
              {
                "key": "Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "idempotent-wallet-test"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"account_id\": \"{{account_id}}\",\n  \"wallet_type\": \"MAIN\",\n  \"currency\": \"COIN\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/wallets",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "wallets"]
            },
            "description": "Tests idempotency: Creating the same wallet multiple times should return the same wallet_id.\n\n**Mechanism:** UNIQUE(account_id, currency, wallet_type) + ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE\n\n**Try this:**\n1. Run this request\n2. Note the wallet_id\n3. Run it again\n4. The wallet_id should be the same"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Same Deposit Twice (Idempotent)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Same idempotency key returns same result\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    console.log(\"Ledger Transaction ID: \" + jsonData.ledger_txn_id);",
                  "    console.log(\"Note: Call this request multiple times with same Idempotency-Key.\");",
                  "    console.log(\"The balance should only increase once, not on every retry.\");",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Id",
                "value": "{{admin_user_id}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-User-Role",
                "value": "ADMIN"
              },
              {
                "key": "Idempotency-Key",
                "value": "idempotent-deposit-fixed-key"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"wallet_id\": \"{{wallet_id}}\",\n  \"amount\": 25,\n  \"currency\": \"COIN\",\n  \"type\": \"manual_deposit\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/wallets/{{wallet_id}}/deposit",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "wallets", "{{wallet_id}}", "deposit"]
            },
            "description": "Tests idempotency: Same deposit with same Idempotency-Key should not double-credit.\n\n**Mechanism:** UNIQUE(idempotency_key) in ledger_txn table\n\n**Try this:**\n1. Note your current balance\n2. Run this request multiple times\n3. Balance should only increase by 25 once (on first call)\n4. Subsequent calls should return the same ledger_txn_id"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Tests to verify idempotency mechanisms.\n\nIdempotency ensures:\n- Safe retries on network failures\n- No duplicate charges/credits\n- Consistent system state\n\nMechanisms:\n1. Wallet: UNIQUE(account_id, currency, wallet_type)\n2. Transactions: UNIQUE(idempotency_key)\n3. Mission Rewards: mission_reward_{reward_grant_id}"
    }
